      "order": 1,
      "Description": "AI is transforming customer support, offering businesses the ability to handle queries faster and at greater scale than ever before. However, deploying AI in customer-facing roles introduces real risks around accuracy, tone, and the trust customers place in your brand. This lesson explores the balance between the efficiency gains AI can deliver and the potential pitfalls that come with automating sensitive interactions. You will learn how to identify where AI adds genuine value, where human oversight remains essential, and how to put practical safeguards in place. By the end, you will have a clearer picture of how to use AI responsibly in your customer support operations.",
